criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients in follow-up in the Hypertension Program (ProHart) at Hospital Universitário
             Clementino Fraga Filho - UFRJ at least six months;

          -  Patient with Resistant Hypertension and Mild Obstructive Sleep Apnea detected by
             polysomnography;

          -  All participants that give written informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age> 85 years;

          -  Cognitive deficit that prevents speech therapy;

          -  Severe clinical events in the last 6 months;

          -  Refusal of the patient to participate in the study;

          -  Pregnancy;

          -  Prior and regular use of CPAP;

          -  Clinical data suggestive of neurological disease with cognitive and / or motor
             sequelae, craniofacial malformation, severe upper airway obstruction, Neuromuscular
             disease, users of hypnotic drugs
